Rating: 3
Great flavor and a welcome change from the 'routine' chicken recipes. Very easy prep -- good for company or quick family meal. Chicken was moist. I made some minor changes -- used sour cream instead of mayo, upped the amount of garlic, green onions and horseradish and used panko bread crumbs. I used boneless skinless chicken breast so I needed to add a little oil to the bread crumb mixture. Will definitely make again. I also think this would be good on fish.

